title: Dorado Beach Collegiate up next for Tech - VT hokiesports.com
content: Dorado Beach Collegiate up next for Tech  VT hokiesports.com
description: Coming off a solid showing in its spring opener, the Virginia Tech men's golf team ventures further south for the Dorado Beach Collegiate hosted by UNC Greensboro at TPC Dorado Beach (par 72, 7,112 yards).
